{"tid":2097540,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"升中派位結果今日公布 統一派位逾八成獲派首三志願","createTime":"2020-07-07T02:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T02:28:32.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9e33ea3ce7bdececb95909038ada642bf81bb66c","tid":2097540,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T02:12:41.000Z","msg":"升中派位結果今日公布 統一派位逾八成獲派首三志願<br />\n2020-07-07 HKT 09:43<br />\n<br />\n&quot;升中派位結果今日公布，今年有54000多名小六學生參加派位，獲自行分配學位的學生中，有63%獲派首志願。統一派位方面，有83%獲派首三志願，62%獲派首志願，分別較去年升4個百分點及5個百分點。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536216-20200707.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536216-20200707.htm&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEpmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=b26c5cbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536216-20200707.htm&h=373bacff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536216-20200707.htm</a>"},{"pid":"eb6b3bc667f066510e595502ca03b8cf988df103","tid":2097540,"uid":128164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T02:28:32.000Z","msg":"原來今日升中派位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}